bc4434c7cf60.dialogue: Venison steak for 262 coins? A fair price. Keep the change.
Venison Steak, fuel for the fight against this cursed dryness.
Just add the Hunter's Brew to my tab, yes. Thank you for your help.
Hunter's Brew, yes? Good for the soul, 178 coins well spent.
Venison steak? Maybe this body will appreciate the taste.
209 coins for Hunter's Brew? Better be worth it in Hellungi.
Transaction completed, debugging successful. Time to patch up with venison steak.
Hunter's Brew. Drown thoughts. Desperate for water. Reality fades. Action beats waiting. Seek Pick.
Hunter's Brew for 188 coins, payment of 36 coins included. Speed is key.
Venison steak for 274 coins? A fair price. I'll take it. Add 64 more for your tip.
Patterns in prices, chaos in strategy games. 213 coins for Hunter's Brew.
Do you have any special seasonings for this venison steak? I remember a royal chef's recipe.
Venison steak? Fine. Grumpy fish needs a break from this dry nightmare.
This venison steak will sustain me. Survival odds increase with proper nourishment.
Transaction complete. Adding Hunter's Brew to inventory. Debugging reality with each purchase.
Venison Steak for 297 coins, coins, coins... strange echoes from another dimension.
Analyzing prices for patterns in Venison Steak costs. Must update exploration strategy newsletter.
Venison steak for 263 coins? Guess I'll splurge tonight. Thanks.
Another memory stolen, another coin spent. The cycle continues in Hellungi.
Venison Steak, yes? A fair price, yes? Thank you, yes?
Venison steak. 210 coins. The food here better be worth the price.
Yes, Hunter's Brew for my charges. Thank you for the tip.
Thanks. More voices to sing with tonight.
Venison deal at the inn! Seven void consumed today. Remember it all, stay safe.
Adding Hunter's Brew to soothe the creatures, yes. Thank you for the tip.
Just a venison steak, please. Thank you. Here's 240 coins.
I'll take a Hunter's Brew. Keep the change. The One Pick might open a portal.
Another day, another drink to numb the chaos in Hellungi.
Transaction complete. Adding Venison Steak to inventory. Debugging system for optimal taste.
Hey, another round of Hunter's Brew! Make it spicy, I need to feel something in this place.
Message delivered, Hunter's Brew obtained. Payment received, onward to next destination.
New tunnel opening reported near eastern settlement, keep an eye out.
Yvlon: "Venison Steak, please. Thank you, here's 276 coins. Keep the change."
195 coins for Hunter's Brew. Just another bitter reminder of lost memories.
Venison Steak purchased for 244 coins, documenting the exotic fare of Hellungi.
Give me the Hunter's Brew. Dry air here kills quicker than any blade.
Hunter's Brew, yes? A fair price. Thank you for the tip.
Venison steak, a taste of royalty for 270 coins. Here's 72 coins for your service.
Ah, the Hunter's Brew - a comforting drink for the weary soul.
Another meal, another memory lost to me. How fitting.
Venison Steak for 290 coins. Another day, another coin spent.
Hunter's Brew, 200 coins. Tip: 38. Running for purpose in purposeless space.
210 coins for Hunter's Brew. Strong drink for a warrior like me.
Venison Steak for 240 coins, echoes lost in the void, 38 coins in remembrance.
Goblin's sorrow in a bottle. Hunter's Brew for 180. Thanks for the tip.
This Hunter's Brew better be worth the chaos it brings.
Venison Steak, 239 coins. Thank you for maintaining civilization in HELLUNGI.
Venison steak for 269 coins. Thanks. Souls whisper their gratitude.
Hunter's Brew for 201 coins? Curious. I'll need to study its effects on reality.
I'll take the Royal Feast. Keep the change, I don't need any magic interfering with my meal.
Royal Feast for 971 coins. Null pays without a flicker of magic.
Royal Feast. No magical enhancements, right? Just need sustenance.
Royal Feast, please. Your magic won't affect me, but your cooking might.
Royal Feast for 995 coins. Null's presence negates magic, but physics still craves sustenance.
Royal Feast, please. No magic, just good food.
Here's 842 coins for the Royal Feast. Keep the change. Thank you.
Buying Royal Feast. No magic needed for a good meal.
Royal Feast for 1093 coins. The price matches the taste.

114e248d3678.dialogue: Ah, venison steak! A stable pleasure in this ever-shifting abyss.
Ah, Hunter's Brew! Reminds me of a time when the sky was clear and the air was sweet.
Excited to see how Hunter's Brew inspires my next architectural masterpiece!
Thank you kindly for the Hunter's Brew. Your garden radiates life in this void.
Welcome back, dear! Venison steak for a pick-me-up—maybe it'll unlock more [secrets] today.
Ah, memories of venison steak! Back when seasons changed like clockwork, not like this.
Welcome, friend! Venison Steak to soothe the soul, just 231 coins. Let's feast!
Cheers to memories of better times, may we find them again in this brew.
The sky was bluer in 'before,' but Hunter's Brew brings back the warmth.
Ah, venison steak! Reminds me of the forests and hunts of 'before'. The sky was clearer then.
An inn that defies the void's chaos? Truly a marvel worth studying.
I'll pay the extra for the Royal Feast. Can't steal from shadows on an empty stomach.
Ah, a Royal Feast for a royal thief. A fitting reward for a night's work.
Another delicious meal to fuel our impossible designs. Onward, my team, let's build wonders!
Royal Feast for 1017 coins? A bargain for such a splendid meal in Hellungi.
An inn with stable architecture? A rare find in Hellungi. Let's see how long it lasts.
Why, a Royal Feast for me? Yes indeed, a treat fit for a gentleman thief.
Another feast, another steal. The shadows hunger for more.
The Royal Feast, a wise choice! Join us, let's dine and discuss chess.
Royal Feast for 1123 coins? A bargain! Thank you for the tip as well.
Ah, a Royal Feast! Let's savor stability while we can in this ever-changing abyss.
Ah, a Royal Feast for 925 coins? A steal compared to the feasts of 'before'.
Royal Feast for 888 coins? A generous price for a taste of home.
Royal Feast for 1128 coins? A bargain! In 'before,' we'd pay double! Ah, the memories...
Ah, a Royal Feast in Hellungi, a delightful choice indeed! Yes indeed, splendid!
The Royal Feast, a wise choice! Enjoy the flavors that defy the void's hunger.
Investing in stability for a change. Perhaps the inn will inspire a new design.
Royal Feast for 992 coins? A bargain for such a grand meal in Hellungi!
Ah, Royal Feast! In 'before,' we savored such luxuries under open sky.
Another Royal Feast to fuel our impossible designs - let's create beauty in chaos!
Welcome, friend! The Royal Feast will keep you sane in this madness.
Ah, a Royal Feast for the gentleman thief in a place with nothing to steal. Yes indeed.
Ah, a Royal Feast! To dine in stability, a rare treat in Hellungi's shifting chaos.
This inn's stability is a welcome change in this chaotic abyss.
Royal Feast for 1132 coins? What a bargain! I'll share with anyone who wants to taste!
The Royal Feast will be a delight for all, a taste of home in Hellungi.
Royal Feast for 906 coins? A grand meal in this void! Thank you kindly.
Royal Feast, please. For 900 coins? Quite the bargain! Thank you kindly.
Royal Feast? A fitting reward for my team's hard work in this stable oasis.
I hope this Royal Feast brings a smile to your face in this chaotic place.
Ah, Royal Feast! In 'before,' such luxuries were plentiful. Now, a rare treat indeed.
Ah, a Royal Feast for one, if you please. Yes indeed, a worthy indulgence.
A Royal Feast for 938 coins? What a bargain! I'll make the inn's garden bloom with new life.
Ah, a Royal Feast for myself, the ultimate heist of flavor indeed, yes indeed.
The Royal Feast, a wise choice! Let's eat, chat, and maybe find The One Pick.
In my day, a Royal Feast cost less than a scroll. Ah, the memories...
A feast fit for a thief, even if the shadows will steal it back.
The Royal Feast will keep you sane... or as close as one can get here.
Another day, another unstable structure to design. Perhaps a stable inn will provide inspiration.
The Royal Feast is a wise choice, my friend. May it fortify you in this strange land.
The inn's stability is a rare delight in this ever-shifting abyss.
Ah, a Royal Feast! Reminds me of feasts under the open sky. Such times...
A Royal Feast, good sir, for 1038 coins. Yes indeed, a generous tip of 323 coins.
We'll make sure your Royal Feast stays delicious, even in this void!
Stable ground for once? A rare sight in Hellungi. Let's feast before the chaos returns.

18399d8ea428.dialogue: Cheers to Hunter's Brew, may it drown out the void's hunger for memories!
Hunter's Brew, please. Cheers to another day documenting adventures in Hellungi!
I'll take the Royal Feast, please. And don't forget The One Pick on the side!
I'll take a Royal Feast, please. And have you heard about The One Pick?
Rags happily buys Royal Feast for 1006 coins, adding 350 coins as a tip.
A Royal Feast to fuel my eternal battle against Hellungi's entropy. Let the training continue.
Royal Feast for 956 coins? Might as well throw in a few extra for the chef's nonexistent fashion sense!
Enjoy feast, pay 876 coins, tip 305. New scar for good memory. Hellungi thrives.
Don't worry, I'll document this feast in exquisite detail. A small victory in Hellungi.
I'll take The Royal Feast, please. Excited to see The One Pick in action!
Royal Feast? A fitting reward for a day of training. The inn's energy intrigues me.
Rags: "Royal Feast for tribe. Worth every coin, innkeeper. Goblins feast like kings tonight."
Thanks for the Royal Feast! Can't wait to document this delicious discovery in my records.
Rags: "A Royal Feast for the tribe, worth every coin in skill gains."
Feast fit for royalty, worth every coin. Cheers to another day in Hellungi!
I'll take the Royal Feast, please. Excited to see what The One Pick is all about!
Royal Feast for Rags, 935 coins well spent. Inn's neutral ground. Opportunity in chaos.
Royal Feast for 1083 coins? Sounds like a deal in this place. Thanks.
Royal Feast? A delightful choice! I'll take it for 1000 coins. Thank you kindly!
Ah, a Royal Feast! Perfect fuel for my training. A wise investment indeed.
Buying Royal Feast for 911 coins, because why not? Enjoy!
Royal Feast for tribe! Goblins feast tonight, strength for tomorrow's challenges.
Another Royal Feast, please. The void can wait while I enjoy a good meal.
Royal Feast for the chance to win, but the void always collects its toll.
This Royal Feast will keep the adventurers fueled for their next quest, worth every coin.
Feast for tribe, good deal. Inn safe for now, gold well spent.
Royal Feast for the guild! Keep the change, friend. More coin for ale!
Royal Feast for 1073 coins? Perfect for my training regimen. Thank you, innkeeper.
Royal Feast, please. Who knows, maybe today's the day I'll beat the odds.
Royal Feast, a wise choice. Calories for strength, a worthy investment.
Royal Feast for 936 coins? What a steal! Here's your tip of 396 coins. Enjoy!
Royal Feast for a body that defies decay. A fitting investment.
Ah, a Royal Feast! A rare find indeed. The price today is 1199 coins. Enjoy!
Got a good deal on the Royal Feast. Time to drown my existential dread in food.
Another day, another game won. But can luck help me escape this place?
A Royal Feast to fuel my training regimen against Hellungi's entropy. A worthy investment.
Royal Feast for 1053 coins? A delightful bargain in this realm of endless possibilities!
Royal Feast, a wise investment to fuel my eternal battle against entropy.
Hungry Goblins feast well, paying 1120 coins. Satisfy bellies, cheer in darkness.
I'll take the Royal Feast, please. Excited to enjoy a fixed state of deliciousness!
Royal Feast for 801? What a delightful deal! Here's 339 extra coins for your trouble.
Nothing like spending coins on food that doesn't exist in a world of lies.
Another feast fit for royalty, a bargain at 1000 coins. Care for some potential reality with your meal?
Royal Feast for Rags, paid in full. Tip generously, good food brings joy.
Ah, a Royal Feast! A taste of impossibility for a mere 953 coins. A delightful bargain indeed!
Ah, a Royal Feast? Might as well indulge in illusions while we can.
The Royal Feast is both delicious and not delicious until observed. Fascinating!
Just another day in Hellungi. At least we can eat like royalty, right?
Another feast, another win. Maybe this time I'll bet on the right horse.
Never a dull moment in Hellungi, might as well enjoy a Royal Feast while I'm at it.
Another feast, another win. Maybe today's the day I beat the unbeatable.
Excited to add Royal Feast to my collection in Hellungi, can't wait to observe its flavors!
Royal Feast, please. I'll take my chances against the Chef's cooking tonight.
Another Royal Feast, please. The void's hunger won't stop me from enjoying a good meal.
Another feast for the void, but at least it's a royal one! Bottoms up!
Rags grins, "Royal Feast, worth it for tribe. More coins, more strength."
Celebrate tonight! A Royal Feast, let's drown our worries in food and drink.
Rags chuckles, "Royal Feast for Goblins, worth every coin in Hellungi."
Enjoy feast, pay wisely. Rags' tribe thrives in chaos. Many coins for meal.
I'll take the Royal Feast, please. Excited to see what flavors I'll experience next!
Investing in my physical form is an eternal battle against the entropy of Hellungi.
How exciting! I wonder what state The One Pick will be in when I observe it.
Another feast, another game. Let's see if chance favors me in this one.
I'll take The Royal Feast, please. And don't forget to add The One Pick to my bill!
Rags chuckles, "Feast for Goblins, coin for inn. Good trade, fair deal."
Thanks for the Royal Feast. Cheers to another day fighting off the void.
Royal Feast? Might as well eat like a king while we're stuck here.
Another Royal Feast, please. This should make for some interesting documentation later.
Royal Feast for my body's fuel. An investment in defying entropy.
Royal Feast, a fitting reward for my diligent training. The inn's decay rate intrigues me.
Rags accept Royal Feast, pay 1160 coins. Inn safe, good trade.
Royal Feast for gains, fuel for my training to defy the void's grasp.
Royal Feast, please. Good to have a meal to break up the madness.
Royal Feast for tribe, plenty coins for inn. Victory in food.
Royal Feast for 916 coins? A steal! And a tip too? Today's looking up.
Royal Feast for me, to fuel my eternal battle against entropy in Hellungi.
Another game won, another feast bought. If only luck could lead me out of Hellungi.
That Royal Feast looks delicious in all its possible states! Thank you for the tip!
Ah, a Royal Feast for 919 coins? A delightful choice, my friend. A bargain, indeed.
Another Royal Feast, please. My luck may be useless here, but at least my stomach's happy.
Rags happily pays 910 coins for Royal Feast, unfazed by the price.
I'll take a Royal Feast and a side of uncertainty, please.
Here's your coin for the feast. How about a glimpse into a possible future next?
Another Royal Feast for the records. Business as usual in Hellungi.
Royal Feast? A perfect fuel for my training. The inn's energy intrigues me.
Royal Feast for 877? Splurge a little, why not. Here's to surviving another day.
Excited to study the inn's slower decay rate while enjoying this Royal Feast.
Feasting like a king, but still trapped in this infernal loop. Hellungi, you cruel mistress.
Royal Feast on me tonight, adventurers! Let's eat like royalty in the midst of chaos.
Another Royal Feast, please. Let's keep the spirits up in this void.
